2005-02-03  William Jon McCann  <mccann@jhu.edu>

	* engines/smooth/src/engine/smooth_gtk2_engine.h: 
	* engines/smooth/src/engine/smooth_gtk2_drawing.c (smooth_draw_flat_box): 
